                    "line_text": "Avec ma mélancolie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "— Voici venir les lilas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Dont le parfum dit : oublie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je demeure seul, hélas !\nAvec ma mélancolie.\n— Voici venir les lilas\nDont le parfum dit : oublie."
